

Main text:
mahājñānarasaiḥ pūrṇo mahāsattveti nigadyate | nityaṃ samayapravṛttatvāt samayasattvo 'bhidhīyate || 5 ||

Apparatus criticus:
pūrṇo] C Na Nb EdS EdT; pūrṇṇa P; pūrṇṇaṃ B K
mahāsattveti] C Na Nb P B; mahāsatvaiti K; mahāsattvo EdS EdT
nityaṃ samayapravṛttatvāt] Σ; nityasa° EdS
samayapravṛttatvāt] Σ; samaye pravṛttatvān K
samayasattvo] C Na P K EdS EdT; samasatvo Nb B

